{"id":104,"parent_id":4,"book_id":4,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":104,"title":"D&C 100","subtitle":"","short_title":"D&C","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Section 100"],[".studyIntro",["i","Revelation given to Joseph Smith the Prophet and Sidney Rigdon, at Perrysburg, New York, October 12, 1833. The two brethren, having been absent from their families for several days, felt some concern about them."]],[".studySummary",["i",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.1-4"},"1–4"],", Joseph and Sidney to preach the gospel for the salvation of souls;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.5-8"},"5–8"],", It will be given them in the very hour what they should say;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.9-12"},"9–12"],", Sidney is to be a spokesman and Joseph is to be a revelator and mighty in testimony;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.13-17"},"13–17"],", The Lord will raise up a pure people, and the obedient will be saved."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.1","order":"06.05.100.12580"},["b","1"],"Verily, thus saith the Lord unto you, my friends Sidney and Joseph, your families are well; they are in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"mine hands"],", and I will do with them as seemeth me good; for in me there is all power."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.2","order":"06.05.100.12581"},["b","2"],"Therefore, follow me, and listen to the counsel which I shall give unto you."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.3","order":"06.05.100.12582"},["b","3"],"Behold, and lo, I have much people in this place, in the regions round about; and an effectual door shall be opened in the regions round about in this eastern land."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.4","order":"06.05.100.12583"},["b","4"],"Therefore, I, the Lord, have suffered you to come unto this place; for thus it was expedient in me for the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"salvation"],"of souls."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.5","order":"06.05.100.12584"},["b","5"],"Therefore, verily I say unto you, lift up your voices unto this people;",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"speak"],"the thoughts that I shall put into your hearts, and you shall not be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"confounded"],"before men;"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.6","order":"06.05.100.12585"},["b","6"],"For it shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"given"],"you in the very hour, yea, in the very moment, what ye shall say."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.7","order":"06.05.100.12586"},["b","7"],"But a commandment I give unto you, that ye shall declare whatsoever thing ye",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"declare"],"in my name, in solemnity of heart, in the spirit of meekness, in all things."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.8","order":"06.05.100.12587"},["b","8"],"And I give unto you this promise, that inasmuch as ye do this the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"Holy Ghost"],"shall be shed forth in bearing record unto all things whatsoever ye shall say."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.9","order":"06.05.100.12588"},["b","9"],"And it is expedient in me that you, my servant Sidney, should be a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"spokesman"],"unto this people; yea, verily, I will ordain you unto this calling, even to be a spokesman unto my servant Joseph."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.10","order":"06.05.100.12589"},["b","10"],"And I will give unto him power to be mighty in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"testimony"],"."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.11","order":"06.05.100.12590"},["b","11"],"And I will give unto thee power to be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"mighty"],"in expounding all scriptures, that thou mayest be a spokesman unto him, and he shall be a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"revelator"],"unto thee, that thou mayest know the certainty of all things",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"pertaining"],"to the things of my kingdom on the earth."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.12","order":"06.05.100.12591"},["b","12"],"Therefore, continue your journey and let your hearts rejoice; for behold, and lo, I am with you even unto the end."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.13","order":"06.05.100.12592"},["b","13"],"And now I give unto you a word concerning Zion.",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"Zion"],"shall be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"redeemed"],", although she is chastened for a little season."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.14","order":"06.05.100.12593"},["b","14"],"Thy brethren, my servants Orson Hyde and John Gould, are in my hands; and inasmuch as they keep my commandments they shall be saved."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.15","order":"06.05.100.12594"},["b","15"],"Therefore, let your hearts be comforted; for",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"all"],"things shall work together for good to them that walk uprightly, and to the sanctification of the church."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.16","order":"06.05.100.12595"},["b","16"],"For I will raise up unto myself a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"pure"],"people, that will serve me in righteousness;"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.17","order":"06.05.100.12596"},["b","17"],"And all that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"call"],"upon the name of the Lord, and keep his commandments, shall be saved. Even so. Amen."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.1a","order":"06.05.100.12597"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/protection-divine"},"TG Protection, Divine"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.4a","order":"06.05.100.12599"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mission-of-latter-day-saints"},"TG Mission of Latter-day Saints"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.5a","order":"06.05.100.12601"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/4.12.12-16"},"Ex. 4:12 (12–16)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/16.1"},"Prov. 16:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/5.18.18-19"},"Hel. 5:18 (18–19)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/13.3"},"13:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/68.3.3-4"},"D&C 68:3 (3–4)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.5b","order":"06.05.100.12603"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.10"},"Acts 6:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.6a","order":"06.05.100.12605"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.19.19-20"},"Matt. 10:19 (19–20)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.85"},"D&C 84:85"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.7a","order":"06.05.100.12607"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/18.21"},"D&C 18:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/43.34"},"43:34"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.61"},"84:61"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.121"},"88:121"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/meek"},"TG Meek"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sincere"},"Sincere"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.8a","order":"06.05.100.12609"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/10.17.13-17"},"Rom. 10:17 (13–17)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/33.1.1-4"},"2 Ne. 33:1 (1–4)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.9a","order":"06.05.100.12611"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/4.16.14-16"},"Ex. 4:16 (14–16)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/3.17.17-18"},"2 Ne. 3:17 (17–18)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/124.104"},"D&C 124:104"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.10a","order":"06.05.100.12613"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/testimony"},"TG Testimony"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.11a","order":"06.05.100.12615"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/18.24"},"Acts 18:24"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/17.3.2-3"},"Alma 17:3 (2–3)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.11b","order":"06.05.100.12617"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/revelation"},"TG Revelation"],"."],["div",{"id":"11c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.11c","order":"06.05.100.12619"},["b","11c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/1.3"},"Acts 1:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.13a","order":"06.05.100.12621"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/zion"},"TG Zion"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.13b","order":"06.05.100.12623"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.99"},"D&C 84:99"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/103.15.15,20,29"},"103:15 (15, 20, 29)"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.15a","order":"06.05.100.12625"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/8.28"},"Rom. 8:28"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.24"},"D&C 90:24"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/105.40"},"105:40"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.16a","order":"06.05.100.12627"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/peculiar-people"},"TG Peculiar People"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/purity"},"Purity"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.17a","order":"06.05.100.12629"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/50.15"},"Ps. 50:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.32"},"Joel 2:32"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/38.5.4-5"},"Alma 38:5 (4–5)"],"."]]}
